      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% on hemolysis index QOI across three mesh refinement levels.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted with coarse (2.1M), medium (5.8M), and fine (14.2M) element meshes. GCI for the scalar stress-based hemolysis index was 2.3%, satisfying the required threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirmed asymptotic convergence. Achieved level exceeds requirement."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
