      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid temperature, hematocrit) documented and traceable to test protocol.",
      "rationale": "All five operating points were tested under controlled laboratory conditions at 37°C with bovine blood at 35% hematocrit. Flow rates and rotational speeds were verified using calibrated instrumentation. Test conditions are fully documented and traceable."
