      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence verified; solver residuals documented for all simulations.",
      "rationale": "All production simulations achieved residual convergence below 1e-5 for continuity and 1e-6 for momentum equations. Pseudo-transient relaxation was applied to stabilize high-speed rotor cases. No divergence events were recorded across 45 simulation runs."
