      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty assessment is not required at Model Risk Level 2 for this context of use. The k-omega SST turbulence model is industry-standard for rotating machinery and has been validated in multiple FDA-sponsored round-robin studies. Scoped out per MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
