      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. Nominal blood viscosity of 0.0035 Pa·s was used. A single-parameter sensitivity analysis on viscosity (±15%) showed less than 3% variation in predicted RH index, confirming low sensitivity to this input."
